Met the MASTER 🤍✨ @imtiazaliofficial 
.
.
Started making instagram poetry videos because of Tamasha and tab se, bus karwaan chal pada hai. Imtiaz Sir undoubtedly has always been a source of inspiration and positivity for me. Watched Chamkila yesterday and tabse just thanking my stars that i got a chance to watch it on a big screen, loved it! Absolute magic. @imtiazaliofficial is back in his magician era! ✨❤️

So much love to my @imtiazali_the_storyteller team 🤝

Samajhna zaroori hai, sharmana nahi..
Periods natural hai, gandagi nahi..
Uspe baat karni hai, usse ghabrana nahi..

This World Menstrual Hygiene Day, let’s be more aware about our Periods and body changes that comes with it. 

I have recently found @sofyclubindia App, that helps me track my periods and also log in any body changes I see. You should give it a try too :)

#sofyclub #menstrualhealth #onedayformenstrualhygiene #awareness #SOFY
